Output demo/demo.gif

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 720
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 45ms

Hide
Type "cd $SPARELOOP_REPO_DIR && export SPARELOOP_HOME=$SPARELOOP_REPO_DIR/demo/.demo-home && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "spareloop suggest"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "spareloop predict"
Enter
Sleep 2500ms

Type "spareloop stats --tool claude"
Enter
Sleep 3500ms

Type "spareloop status --tool claude"
Enter
Sleep 2500ms

Type "spareloop list"
Enter
Sleep 2500ms
